Italy’s labor market needs more
“fluidity,”  Vodafone Group Plc (VOD)  Chief Executive Officer
 Vittorio Colao  said at a conference in Milan hosted by
Confindustria, a lobby for the country’s employers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
